      public ComboBoxBuilder<T> stringRenderer(Function<@Nullable T,String> stringRenderer)
      Sets the function used to render the items in the combo box as strings. This function is used to convert each item of type T into its textual representation for display in the combo box.

      Note: the supplied function must correctly handle null values.

      Parameters:
      stringRenderer - a Function that accepts an item of type T and returns its corresponding string representation

      this instance of ComboBoxBuilder for method chaining
